%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant O as Omnibox
    participant Net as Browser nav

    U->>O: Type "j 123" + space
    O->>O: Lookup "j" in site-search registry
    O->>O: Match → Jira template, enter search mode
    U->>O: Press Enter
    O->>O: Substitute %s with "123"
    O->>Net: Navigate to resolved URL
    Net-->>U: Jira ticket page
